                            <comment id="16608537" author="mshuler" created="Sun, 9 Sep 2018 18:48:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached&#160;&lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12938997/12938997_CASSANDRA-14710_c.in.sh.patch.txt&quot; title=&quot;CASSANDRA-14710_c.in.sh.patch.txt attached to CASSANDRA-14710&quot;&gt;CASSANDRA-14710_c.in.sh.patch.txt&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; to drop separate debian/cassandra.in.sh file and install quilt-patched bin/cassandra.in.sh.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Github branch is here: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/mshuler/cassandra/tree/CASSANDRA-14710_c.in.sh&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/mshuler/cassandra/tree/CASSANDRA-14710_c.in.sh&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16833757" author="jan karlsson" created="Mon, 6 May 2019 12:23:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Took a look at the patch and LGTM. Seems to all apply cleanly and installs just fine in a Debian docker container.&lt;/p&gt;

